            "title": "Infants (6 weeks \u2013 12 months)",
            "description": "<p>Gentle sensory exploration, tummy time, and one-on-one bonding. Dedicated caregivers follow each baby's natural schedule for feeding, napping, and play. A calm, secure space that helps infants build trust and attachment.</p>"
