          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Toddlers (1 \u2013 2 years)",
            "description": "<p>Active discovery through music, movement, art, and early language. Structured routines build confidence and independence while giving toddlers the freedom to explore at their own pace. Small group sizes ensure every child is seen.</p>"
